<br>
She sighs again knowing that her goal of achieving her Epic is going to take away her time from her guildmates and from raids with the other guilds that have been befriended.  With a weary heart she quaffs (I just love that word) her Honey Mead and jumps off the platform allowing her Safe Fall ability save her from massive damage.<br>
<br>
